    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your mastery of your body gives you the following benefits:</p><p><strong>Poison Immunity.</strong> You are immune to Poison damage and the Poisoned conditions</p><p><strong>Inexhaustible.</strong> You have Advantage on saving throws to avoid or end Exhaustion</p><p><strong>Dexterous Adaptability.</strong> You may use your Dexterity modifier in place of your Strength modifier for any Strength ability check</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-iaNPA9knNh6zGFD1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>When you receive this feature, you can change manually change any Strength skills to Dexterity if you wish.</p></section>",
